&lt;pre class=&#34;language-html&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;button&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;token attr-name&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token attr-value&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation attr-equals&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;js-classily&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;token attr-name&#34;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token attr-value&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation attr-equals&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;button&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;token attr-name&#34;&gt;data-target&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token attr-value&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation attr-equals&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;.my-class&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;token attr-name&#34;&gt;data-class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token attr-value&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation attr-equals&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;blue&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;  Toggle class&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;button&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;...&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;h1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;token attr-name&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token attr-value&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation attr-equals&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;my-class&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;h1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;h1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;token attr-name&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token attr-value&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation attr-equals&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;my-class&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;h1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By adding the same class &lt;code&gt;.my-class&lt;/code&gt; on target elements we are targeting both headings at the same time. That is because Classily.js uses &lt;code&gt;querySelectorAll()&lt;/code&gt; function.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is another way how we could achieve the same effect—we could provide a comma-separated list of selectors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;How to toggle multiple classes on multiple elements?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the example below, we are toggling two different classes on two separate elements.&lt;/p&gt;
